\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Layer-wise personality encoding profile for Openness.} \emph  {Left:} Linear probe accuracy (all layers achieve near-perfect separability). \emph  {Center:} Mean difference norm grows exponentially through layers, peaking at Layer~26 before dropping at the final layer. \emph  {Right:} PCA explained variance shows initial concentration (Layer~0), dispersion, and re-focusing in middle layers.}}{6}{figure.caption.18}\protected@file@percent }
